race.description: Peter Kittle Toyota Para Hills Free For All Pr2 Di
race.comment: BINNAWAY MIRAGE (2) is a progressive type who recorded his 11th career win last time out (22.53) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Looks to have an edge on most of these. PRIME VOLTAGE (8) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 5 three back before a placing at this track the following run. Has the ability and can find best this time. TOWN STRANGER (7) ran below his best last time finishing fourth (23.23) over 400m at this track in a Grade 5. Solid record here winning six races. Great chance to atone. LONG GULLY ASH (1) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.
